public static sealed interface LogProperties.PropertyGetter.RequiredPropertyGetter<T> extends LogProperties.PropertyGetter.ChildPropertyGetter<T>
A property getter that guarantees the result will not be missing usually because a non-null fallback is provided somewhere.
